title: Tour France 2015 The Game v1.3.3
description:
The official game of the Tour de France!
Enjoy the best cycling simulation on your phone or tablet.

This year, try our new features: create your own team, team power presentation on the new multiplayer mode, choose your cyclists and buy new, new animations and resources for more realism! Choose your team, run by the 21 official stages and have fun!

------------------------------------

The Tour de France 2015 is approaching and you feel that his riders are getting nervous. They rely on you for the next races. You encouraged them for months, asking them to surpass themselves and of these the best, ... you know the strengths and weaknesses of each.

You know the stages of this new issue deeply. And all this work can not be thrown away. You set goals for yourself and also the yellow jersey is the goal number 1. His name is at stake.

Do you want to impose their own style on the Tour de France in 2015 and cycling. You will be revealed during the race. And for this, you will manage your cyclists as well as a passionate leader does
